# PhotogrammetrySession.Output.requestError(_:_:)

**Case**

The session aborted a request due to an error.

## Declaration

```swift
case requestError(PhotogrammetrySession.Request, any Error)
```

## Parameters

- **Request**: The request in progress.
- **Error**: Details of the error.

## Monitoring request status

- **PhotogrammetrySession.Output.requestProgress(_:fractionComplete:)**: A progress update provided by the session.
- **PhotogrammetrySession.Output.requestComplete(_:_:)**: The session finished handling all pending requests.
